data.description: Excellent Opportunity!! Motivated Seller!Huge corner lot that sits on 2.79 Acres! Great Opportunity to add an ADU or use for your farm animals, and Big enough lot for all your toys! Home was updated in 2018 with a new A/C Unit, new flooring, updated bathrooms, updated kitchen, new windows, and new roof.  It also has both city water and electric.Not far from the Devils Punchbowl.  Do not miss out on the spectacular mountain views and indescribable sunsets! Enjoy the home with so much peace and tranquility from a long day of work. Buyer to investigate and satisfy themselves as to the square footage and all additional information. Seller, Broker and Broker's agents do not represent or guarantee the accuracy of the square footage, bedroom/bathroom count, lot size or lot lines, permitted or non permitted spaces. Buyer(s) & Buyer's agents are advised to independently verify the accuracy of all info and to do their own due diligence''.
